---
title: One-Pan Pineapple Salsa Pork Tacos with Cilantro & Sour Cream
description: Looking for a new way to spice-up your taco Tuesday (or Wednesday... or, any day of the week, really!)? Our chefs put together a sweet and savory version that’s sure to satisfy. There’s richly-spiced ground pork cooked in pineapple juice, plus charred pepper and onion, a pineapple salsa, and cooling sour cream, all piled into flour tortillas. Taco’bout a great meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/643ecb83e84becd3520a85dd-1a4890df.jpg
